edit profile information:
If the user is logged in and would like to edit their profile information, then they can click on the view profile button on the menu. In the case where the user is not logged in they will be prompted to login. Once they are on the profile page they can see the information which the system currently has about them and click on a button to which will allow them to edit that information, outside of email address and username. If they want to add a profile picture they can click on their current profile picture, or default profile picture if not previously set and upload a new profile picture. After they have finished editing the information to their liking the user can submit the information using a button on the bottom of the page which will edit the information in the database to match the new information which they added.
